[SN]TITLE[SN]
Body of missing Orkney man Boyd Livingstone found

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The body of a man missing since heading out on a fishing trip with his brother has been found.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Boyd and Andrew Livingstone failed to return from a trip in the Loch of Boardhouse area of Orkney on 2 August.
The alarm was raised by family and the body of Andrew, 71, was later found in the loch.
Police said a second body recovered after a report from a member of the public at about 17:00 on Sunday had been identified as Boyd, who was 68.
